Class ArdenusManifest

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.jar.Manifest
      • org.ardenus.ArdenusManifest
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable

    public class ArdenusManifest
extends java.util.jar.Manifest
    Represents an Ardenus manifest file which is used to determine information about the game and how it should be ran.
    Author:
    Trent "Whirvis" Summerlin
